    "causal_summary": "Packet 014 extracted code-graph ownership into `.opencode/skills/system-code-graph/`, but its TypeScript config kept both an `include` for `../system-spec-kit/shared/**/*.ts` and a project `references` entry for `../system-spec-kit/shared`. With project references active, TypeScript treated the shared project as owning its own emitted output, so a clean system-code-graph build typechecked those files without placing `shared/*.js` under `dist/system-spec-kit/shared/`.",
